title nasim — MEM-03 SEARCH Knowledge

' Participants with box colors per C4 layer

note over participants
  Scope:          Full-text search across all knowledge
  Preconditions:  MemoryIndex populated with entries
  Excludes:       Direct key recall (MEM-02)
  Contexts:       Agent memory search, cross-project discovery
  Rollback:       No rollback needed (read-only operation)
  Design:         BM25 ranking with relevance scoring
end note

== MEM-03 SEARCH Knowledge ==

AgentOrchestrator -> MemoryIndex: search(query, filters)
MemoryIndex -> MemoryIndex: tokenize query
MemoryIndex -> MemoryIndex: FTS5 query with BM25 ranking
MemoryIndex -> MemoryIndex: rank results by relevance
MemoryIndex --> AgentOrchestrator: ranked_results

note over participants
  Flow:    Tokenize -> FTS5 query -> rank -> return
  State:   searching -> ranking -> returned
  Failure: No results -> return empty list, log query
  Success: Agent receives ranked search results
end note

@enduml